c: 12
v: 36
t: "And there two (other) young men (also) came with him into the prison. One of them said: \"I see me (in a dream) pressing (grapes for) wine.\" The other one said: \"I see me (in a dream) carrying bread on my head, and birds are eating from it.\" (They both said): \"Tell us the truth and meaning of it (all): Verily, we see that you are the one who does good (for everyone)"